Jason Powers, Managing Director, WELLS FARGO




10:00 AM  Keynote Address “Important Legislative Developments and Their Potential Impact on the CLO Market" 



Neil Weidner, Partner, CADWALADER, WICKERSHAM & TAFT LLP
The Honorable Congressman Andy Barr, , THE UNITED STATES HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES




10:45 AM  Networking Refreshment Break in Exhibit Area 





11:15 AM Track A How Risk Retention will Shape the CLO Market: Implementation and Compliance Considerations 


Overview of the key highlights of the rule and impact on the CLO marketPractical tips for achieving compliance while maximizing efficiency, and minimizing costThe legal and accounting viewpoint: how should managers comply? How will managers hold the risk, and recapitalize?How can CLO managers ensure their structures are compliant? Creating a global product: Can a 'super-structure' be developed that will also comply with European CRD IV requirements?





Edmond Seferi, Partner, MORGAN, LEWIS & BOCKIUS LLP (Moderator)
