How have banks' leveraged lending guidelines changed in the last 12 months? Have underwriting standards tightened amid less appetite for risk? Does this mean lower asset supply and what will be the impact on arbitrage for CLO managers?Assessing credit quality of the underlying assetsSpread levelsVolume and diversity outlookUpdate on M&A activity





