About Us





Swimming pool loans are unique – why not use a company whose specialty is pool financing? Lyon Financial has been a partner with the swimming pool and home improvement industry for over 38 years. We provide access to unique financing solutions for families nationwide who are looking to create the backyard of their dreams. Lyon Financial can suggest sources of funds based depending on the consumer’s needs and qualifications, eliminating a lengthy and stressful stereotypical loan process.
Not only will our dedicated team of professionals find the best solution for your needs, they will also be there until your project is complete. Building a swimming pool can take up to several months to complete, and there are many factors that could affect the construction process. This may be your first swimming pool, but we have managed over 400,000. Let us help you every step of the way until you and your family are swimming in your sparkling new pool.
At the heart of Lyon Financial’s success is our outstanding customer service. Our clients know that an actual project manager will answer the phone when they call. They also know that we provide individual attention from start to finish; while tailoring solutions to meet the specific needs of each and every client.
We are very proud of our reputation and strive to help every customer who consults us for financing.
Contact any of our team members for more information on how we can help make your backyard dream come true.





We love the difference we can make for your family by providing something that puts years of memories within reach. Call 877-754-5966 today!


